1
00:00:54,479 --> 00:00:55,560
Cut the crap!

2
00:00:56,280 --> 00:00:57,039
Pay me!

3
00:00:57,640 --> 00:00:58,159
Or

4
00:00:58,679 --> 00:01:00,640
I'll sell you to the brothel!

5
00:01:00,799 --> 00:01:01,159
You...

6
00:01:01,640 --> 00:01:01,960
Let me go!

7
00:01:08,959 --> 00:01:09,920
Enjoy yourselves.

8
00:01:11,359 --> 00:01:12,560
The bill for today's wine

9
00:01:12,959 --> 00:01:14,159
and the horse rental,

10
00:01:14,599 --> 00:01:15,760
how much do you need in total?

11
00:01:16,359 --> 00:01:17,640
I'll send someone to you tomorrow.

12
00:01:17,920 --> 00:01:19,120
Don't worry, I'll definitely pay up.

13
00:01:20,359 --> 00:01:20,920
Or,

14
00:01:21,280 --> 00:01:22,319
I can write you a note first.

15
00:01:22,799 --> 00:01:24,079
The earrings you gave me earlier

16
00:01:24,480 --> 00:01:25,599
could buy this entire tavern.

17
00:01:26,040 --> 00:01:26,719
No need for a note.

18
00:01:27,799 --> 00:01:28,280
It's no big deal.

19
00:01:28,920 --> 00:01:29,239
Miss,

20
00:01:29,480 --> 00:01:29,920
don't worry about it.

21
00:01:33,200 --> 00:01:34,079
From your

22
00:01:34,120 --> 00:01:35,159
appearance,

23
00:01:36,040 --> 00:01:37,319
you're no ordinary folk.

24
00:01:38,400 --> 00:01:39,040
I reckon

25
00:01:39,359 --> 00:01:40,599
you're not short of a few copper coins.

26
00:01:42,480 --> 00:01:43,159
I apologize for

27
00:01:43,280 --> 00:01:43,840
the offense today.

28
00:01:44,480 --> 00:01:45,000
This drink

29
00:01:45,359 --> 00:01:46,079
is to make amends.

30
00:01:46,840 --> 00:01:48,239
If you ever need anything in the future,

31
00:01:48,640 --> 00:01:49,280
just come to me.

32
00:01:59,480 --> 00:02:00,280
Forgive my bluntness.

33
00:02:01,400 --> 00:02:01,920
Today

34
00:02:02,560 --> 00:02:03,680
supposed to be your wedding day.

35
00:02:04,719 --> 00:02:06,519
Why are you drinking alone here at night?

36
00:02:19,080 --> 00:02:19,719
Do you believe in fate?

37
00:02:20,919 --> 00:02:21,520
You mean

38
00:02:22,039 --> 00:02:22,520
fortune-telling?

39
00:02:26,479 --> 00:02:27,280
To be honest,

40
00:02:28,360 --> 00:02:29,120
I once

41
00:02:29,960 --> 00:02:31,319
had a very

42
00:02:32,039 --> 00:02:32,680
long dream.

43
00:02:33,759 --> 00:02:34,360
In the dream,

44
00:02:34,800 --> 00:02:35,759
I was plagued by bad luck.

45
00:02:37,280 --> 00:02:38,479
My mother died first.

46
00:02:39,639 --> 00:02:40,120
Then

47
00:02:41,159 --> 00:02:42,240
my family died.

48
00:02:43,360 --> 00:02:44,280
And finally,

49
00:02:45,199 --> 00:02:46,120
I died too.

50
00:02:50,639 --> 00:02:52,479
If you knew your life

51
00:02:53,400 --> 00:02:54,319
would be full of misfortune,

52
00:02:54,919 --> 00:02:55,759
and you couldn't change it,

53
00:02:57,080 --> 00:02:57,879
what would you do?

54
00:03:00,759 --> 00:03:01,520
Do you know

55
00:03:02,120 --> 00:03:03,280
a kind of plant called Pubudin?

56
00:03:04,599 --> 00:03:05,439
It has no roots,

57
00:03:06,000 --> 00:03:06,680
and adapts to any environment.

58
00:03:07,960 --> 00:03:09,000
Even a gust of wind

59
00:03:09,599 --> 00:03:10,879
can roll it into a whirlpool.

60
00:03:12,080 --> 00:03:12,960
But even so,

61
00:03:13,919 --> 00:03:16,120
it is more tenacious than those towering trees.

62
00:03:16,919 --> 00:03:17,800
No matter where it drifts,

63
00:03:18,680 --> 00:03:20,520
it will find a place to settle.

64
00:03:22,199 --> 00:03:23,800
You just asked me if I believe in fate.

65
00:03:24,919 --> 00:03:26,159
But compared to leaving it to fate,

66
00:03:27,120 --> 00:03:28,719
I believe more in man's victory over nature.

67
00:03:30,199 --> 00:03:30,960
Man

68
00:03:31,599 --> 00:03:32,360
can conquer nature.

69
00:03:35,719 --> 00:03:37,199
Even if I still marry

70
00:03:37,199 --> 00:03:38,319
the Second Prince as in my dream,

71
00:03:39,159 --> 00:03:39,840
now,

72
00:03:40,759 --> 00:03:41,759
I'm not foolish,

73
00:03:42,080 --> 00:03:42,879
my parents are healthy,

74
00:03:43,560 --> 00:03:44,680
and the Prime Minister's Residence is safe.

75
00:03:45,680 --> 00:03:46,879
Even if things go wrong,

76
00:03:47,560 --> 00:03:48,919
it's better than sitting and waiting to die.

77
00:03:52,639 --> 00:03:53,759
It's nice to talk to you.

78
00:03:54,159 --> 00:03:54,840
But I don't know

79
00:03:54,919 --> 00:03:55,800
your name.

80
00:03:58,879 --> 00:03:59,520
I'm Lou Xi.

81
00:04:01,360 --> 00:04:02,159
Mr. Lou,

82
00:04:06,080 --> 00:04:06,919
it's getting late.

83
00:04:07,639 --> 00:04:08,439
I'll go back to the mansion.

84
00:04:09,240 --> 00:04:10,159
See you later.

85
00:04:21,800 --> 00:04:22,800
[These eyes]

86
00:04:24,000 --> 00:04:24,959
[look so familiar.]

87
00:04:34,639 --> 00:04:35,079
Chu,

88
00:04:36,279 --> 00:04:37,480
Shen Suhe is the principal consort

89
00:04:37,879 --> 00:04:38,720
by the will of my father.

90
00:04:39,920 --> 00:04:40,399
I swear

91
00:04:41,000 --> 00:04:42,279
I only have you in my heart.

92
00:04:45,000 --> 00:04:47,199
You just use these sweet words to fool me.

93
00:04:47,800 --> 00:04:49,040
Even if you are not happy,

94
00:04:49,600 --> 00:04:50,439
Shen Suhe

95
00:04:50,800 --> 00:04:52,399
is the principal consort in name.

96
00:04:53,399 --> 00:04:54,720
I'm just a concubine.

97
00:04:55,720 --> 00:04:57,240
If we sleep together tonight,

98
00:04:58,000 --> 00:04:59,319
she must be thinking about

99
00:04:59,319 --> 00:05:00,560
how to establish her authority over me.

100
00:05:03,079 --> 00:05:03,839
Chu, don't worry.

101
00:05:04,720 --> 00:05:06,199
I've already told everyone in the mansion

102
00:05:07,279 --> 00:05:07,680
that from now on,

103
00:05:08,199 --> 00:05:08,959
you are the most important.

104
00:05:09,720 --> 00:05:10,800
Just treat her as a decoration.

105
00:05:14,759 --> 00:05:15,800
I'll trust you this time.

106
00:05:17,040 --> 00:05:17,839
Just thinking about

107
00:05:18,399 --> 00:05:20,319
her tossing and turning tonight

108
00:05:21,319 --> 00:05:22,240
is quite satisfying.

109
00:05:23,800 --> 00:05:24,560
How about

110
00:05:25,480 --> 00:05:26,279
we make her even angrier?

111
00:05:31,319 --> 00:05:32,319
You're so bad.

112
00:05:35,160 --> 00:05:35,639
Ruirui,

113
00:05:36,199 --> 00:05:37,160
bring some tea.

114
00:05:49,199 --> 00:05:49,680
Miss,

115
00:05:50,439 --> 00:05:51,839
I just saw the princess

116
00:05:52,480 --> 00:05:53,560
sneaking out of the mansion.

117
00:05:54,279 --> 00:05:54,839
What did you say?

118
00:05:56,120 --> 00:05:56,600
Chu,

119
00:06:00,360 --> 00:06:00,920
you go out first.

120
00:06:05,879 --> 00:06:06,480
What are you talking about?

121
00:06:08,439 --> 00:06:09,040
Your Highness,

122
00:06:09,959 --> 00:06:11,040
Shen Suhe

123
00:06:11,480 --> 00:06:12,680
is the Prime Minister's daughter.

124
00:06:13,600 --> 00:06:14,639
As a new member of the family,

125
00:06:15,000 --> 00:06:16,920
you should go and see her.

126
00:06:17,319 --> 00:06:19,279
Otherwise, His Majesty will be

127
00:06:19,560 --> 00:06:20,279
displeased.

128
00:06:21,800 --> 00:06:23,639
I just lost my temper.

129
00:06:24,240 --> 00:06:25,040
I don't want

130
00:06:25,399 --> 00:06:27,079
you to be punished because of me.

131
00:06:27,879 --> 00:06:28,319
Chu,

132
00:06:29,160 --> 00:06:30,199
you're sensible.

133
00:06:31,319 --> 00:06:32,560
Let's go as you said.

134
00:06:33,000 --> 00:06:33,560
By the way,

135
00:06:34,480 --> 00:06:35,800
teach her the rules of the mansion.

136
00:06:41,959 --> 00:06:43,000
Sure enough,

137
00:06:43,720 --> 00:06:44,800
only food

138
00:06:45,600 --> 00:06:46,639
can save me.

139
00:06:47,959 --> 00:06:49,639
Here comes Prince Rui.

140
00:06:50,279 --> 00:06:50,800
Prince Rui

141
00:06:54,920 --> 00:06:55,399
Oh, no.

142
00:06:56,360 --> 00:06:57,319
She hasn't come back yet.

143
00:07:07,680 --> 00:07:08,519
Is the Princess inside?

144
00:07:09,120 --> 00:07:09,759
I'm here to see her.

145
00:07:10,079 --> 00:07:10,920
My Lady.

146
00:07:13,120 --> 00:07:13,720
Your Highness,

147
00:07:14,199 --> 00:07:14,839
the Princess

148
00:07:15,120 --> 00:07:15,560
is asleep.

149
00:07:16,120 --> 00:07:16,600
Asleep?

150
00:07:17,399 --> 00:07:18,639
But the light is still on.

151
00:07:19,079 --> 00:07:19,639
Is it possible that

152
00:07:20,279 --> 00:07:21,639
she doesn't want to see me?

153
00:07:22,920 --> 00:07:23,480
Your Highness,

154
00:07:23,959 --> 00:07:24,800
the Princess

155
00:07:25,519 --> 00:07:26,240
is afraid of the dark.

156
00:07:26,680 --> 00:07:28,439
So she always sleeps with the candle on.

157
00:07:28,720 --> 00:07:30,160
She's the Prime Minister's daughter.

158
00:07:30,680 --> 00:07:32,079
But she went to bed

159
00:07:32,199 --> 00:07:33,439
before you.

160
00:07:33,959 --> 00:07:35,199
What a bad manner!

161
00:07:35,959 --> 00:07:37,160
The Princess waited for you all night,

162
00:07:37,759 --> 00:07:38,839
and didn't even eat anything.

163
00:07:39,600 --> 00:07:40,519
Who knows

164
00:07:40,519 --> 00:07:41,879
which woman has been pestering you?

165
00:07:41,879 --> 00:07:42,839
You wicked maid!

166
00:07:43,439 --> 00:07:44,600
What kind of master

167
00:07:44,800 --> 00:07:45,839
what kind of servant!

168
00:07:45,959 --> 00:07:46,399
Rui

169
00:07:47,120 --> 00:07:48,560
Teach her some manners.

170
00:07:49,279 --> 00:07:49,639
Yes.

171
00:07:50,279 --> 00:07:52,079
I'm the maid of the Princess.

172
00:07:53,120 --> 00:07:54,319
You are just a concubine.

173
00:07:54,519 --> 00:07:55,600
How dare you teach me?

174
00:07:57,279 --> 00:07:57,759
Your Highness,

175
00:07:57,759 --> 00:07:58,759
this is Prince Rui's Mansion.

176
00:07:59,279 --> 00:08:00,560
You should be punished for disrespecting the master.

177
00:08:01,000 --> 00:08:01,360
Slap her!

178
00:08:06,319 --> 00:08:08,439
The noise didn't wake up the Princess.

179
00:08:09,160 --> 00:08:09,920
Could it be that

180
00:08:10,199 --> 00:08:11,360
the Princess isn't inside?

181
00:08:11,879 --> 00:08:12,600
Your Highness,

182
00:08:13,000 --> 00:08:14,120
I heard that

183
00:08:14,439 --> 00:08:15,040
during the day,

184
00:08:15,519 --> 00:08:16,920
the Princess rode a horse

185
00:08:17,000 --> 00:08:18,560
on a horse to the mansion.

186
00:08:21,879 --> 00:08:24,079
She's not here on our wedding night.

187
00:08:24,720 --> 00:08:25,600
Could she

188
00:08:25,959 --> 00:08:27,279
have slipped out to meet someone?

189
00:08:28,199 --> 00:08:28,800
Nonsense!

190
00:08:29,240 --> 00:08:30,319
She's already asleep.

191
00:08:30,319 --> 00:08:30,680
Asleep?

192
00:08:31,439 --> 00:08:32,240
Then wake her up.

193
00:08:32,720 --> 00:08:33,639
Who's there?

194
00:08:34,080 --> 00:08:34,840
Making all that noise,

195
00:08:34,840 --> 00:08:35,759
ruining my good dream.

196
00:08:37,120 --> 00:08:37,879
My Lady,

197
00:08:38,840 --> 00:08:39,559
His Highness is here.

198
00:08:41,000 --> 00:08:42,080
I didn't greet you properly.

199
00:08:42,480 --> 00:08:43,279
Please forgive me.

200
00:08:44,480 --> 00:08:45,320
Why are you in here?

201
00:08:47,679 --> 00:08:48,720
This is my chamber.

202
00:08:49,159 --> 00:08:50,039
Shouldn't I be in here?

203
00:08:56,960 --> 00:08:57,600
You're drunk.

204
00:09:03,120 --> 00:09:03,600
I'm sorry.

205
00:09:04,399 --> 00:09:04,960
It's late.

206
00:09:05,399 --> 00:09:06,080
I'll take you home.

207
00:09:10,080 --> 00:09:11,279
It's Prince Rui's Mansion.

208
00:09:11,840 --> 00:09:13,039
I can't go further.

209
00:09:13,639 --> 00:09:14,399
Please go back.

210
00:09:16,399 --> 00:09:17,039
Mr. Lou,

211
00:09:17,759 --> 00:09:19,000
I have one more request.

212
00:09:26,600 --> 00:09:27,840
If you don't let go,

213
00:09:28,279 --> 00:09:29,399
we'll be found.

214
00:09:34,679 --> 00:09:35,440
Thank you.

215
00:09:40,480 --> 00:09:41,360
Lou Xi.

216
00:09:42,919 --> 00:09:43,440
It's impossible.

217
00:09:46,480 --> 00:09:48,440
[What does she want from me?]

218
00:09:49,399 --> 00:09:50,360
Shen Suhe,

219
00:09:51,480 --> 00:09:52,679
have you really stayed in the palace

220
00:09:52,679 --> 00:09:53,639
and never gone out?

221
00:09:54,000 --> 00:09:55,200
Did anyone see you

222
00:09:55,440 --> 00:09:56,519
sneaking out?

223
00:09:58,360 --> 00:10:00,279
I didn't stay in the palace all the time.

224
00:10:01,200 --> 00:10:03,120
I drank too much water before bed

225
00:10:03,480 --> 00:10:04,480
and had to go to the bathroom.

226
00:10:04,720 --> 00:10:05,399
I had to go out.

227
00:10:05,679 --> 00:10:05,879
You...

228
00:10:05,879 --> 00:10:06,440
Shen Suhe,

229
00:10:07,000 --> 00:10:07,960
as you married into the Prince's Mansion,

230
00:10:08,080 --> 00:10:09,080
you should abide by the rules here.

231
00:10:09,399 --> 00:10:10,440
You should watch your words and actions.

232
00:10:11,960 --> 00:10:12,639
I think

233
00:10:13,000 --> 00:10:14,039
what I said and did

234
00:10:14,320 --> 00:10:15,399
was not out of line.

235
00:10:16,399 --> 00:10:17,480
But you

236
00:10:18,200 --> 00:10:19,320
neglected your wife

237
00:10:19,720 --> 00:10:20,759
on your wedding night,

238
00:10:21,080 --> 00:10:21,919
favored the concubine over the principal wife.

239
00:10:22,440 --> 00:10:23,720
If this reaches His Majesty's ears,

240
00:10:24,200 --> 00:10:25,200
he might think

241
00:10:25,639 --> 00:10:26,639
you are dissatisfied

242
00:10:26,639 --> 00:10:27,720
with this marriage.

243
00:10:31,559 --> 00:10:32,039
Your Highness,

244
00:10:32,399 --> 00:10:33,200
you're finally back.

245
00:10:33,639 --> 00:10:34,879
I thought something happened to you.

246
00:10:35,120 --> 00:10:36,120
I was just about to look for you.

247
00:10:40,600 --> 00:10:41,759
You've been drinking.

248
00:10:46,360 --> 00:10:47,240
It's not just alcohol.

249
00:10:49,440 --> 00:10:50,159
There's also

250
00:10:51,200 --> 00:10:52,960
a hint of rouge.

251
00:10:54,399 --> 00:10:55,000
Your Highness,

252
00:10:55,519 --> 00:10:56,720
you haven't touched a drop

253
00:10:57,080 --> 00:10:58,320
since leaving the barracks.

254
00:10:59,000 --> 00:10:59,960
How come tonight,

255
00:11:00,279 --> 00:11:01,320
you drank with a woman?

256
00:11:03,840 --> 00:11:04,799
Did you go to...

257
00:11:05,519 --> 00:11:06,279
I didn't expect

258
00:11:06,960 --> 00:11:08,320
you have a dog's nose.

259
00:11:09,120 --> 00:11:10,240
It's a waste

260
00:11:10,320 --> 00:11:11,039
to stay by my side.

261
00:11:13,639 --> 00:11:14,360
Where's the thing

262
00:11:14,519 --> 00:11:15,120
I asked you to investigate?

263
00:11:16,039 --> 00:11:16,799
You should

264
00:11:16,960 --> 00:11:17,799
trust me.

265
00:11:19,519 --> 00:11:20,200
However,

266
00:11:21,440 --> 00:11:22,720
I see Your Highness are so busy,

267
00:11:22,960 --> 00:11:23,960
but still come to see me.

268
00:11:24,519 --> 00:11:25,600
I think what you said just now

269
00:11:25,600 --> 00:11:26,759
is all nonsense.

270
00:11:27,480 --> 00:11:29,399
If you and the concubine

271
00:11:29,559 --> 00:11:30,519
have nothing else to do,

272
00:11:31,480 --> 00:11:32,559
I'll go back and rest.

273
00:11:33,240 --> 00:11:33,559
Zhiyan,

274
00:11:33,879 --> 00:11:34,159
send her away.

275
00:11:35,320 --> 00:11:35,639
Please.

276
00:11:38,240 --> 00:11:38,519
By the way,

277
00:11:39,080 --> 00:11:40,000
Concubine Chuchu,

278
00:11:40,840 --> 00:11:41,960
in this long night,

279
00:11:42,360 --> 00:11:43,399
you should be careful.

280
00:11:43,879 --> 00:11:44,919
Don't tire yourself out.

281
00:11:45,559 --> 00:11:45,879
You...

282
00:11:50,679 --> 00:11:51,200
The officials

283
00:11:51,440 --> 00:11:52,440
of the fifth-rank and above

284
00:11:52,559 --> 00:11:53,159
are all recorded here.

285
00:11:54,159 --> 00:11:54,879
Although

286
00:11:55,000 --> 00:11:56,320
Prime Minister Shen leads the six ministries,

287
00:11:56,840 --> 00:11:58,360
His Majesty has not yet named a Crown Prince.

288
00:11:58,960 --> 00:12:00,000
Half of the officials

289
00:12:00,279 --> 00:12:02,000
have privately recognized Prince Rui as the Crown Prince.

290
00:12:03,200 --> 00:12:03,720
Now,

291
00:12:04,000 --> 00:12:04,720
on the court,

292
00:12:05,039 --> 00:12:06,159
Prince Rui and Prime Minister Shen

293
00:12:06,320 --> 00:12:07,320
are evenly matched.

294
00:12:08,519 --> 00:12:09,039
Since

295
00:12:09,279 --> 00:12:10,120
you and General Xiao

296
00:12:10,120 --> 00:12:11,879
have known that someone colluded with the enemy

297
00:12:12,240 --> 00:12:13,399
to deliberately provoke a war,

298
00:12:14,080 --> 00:12:15,399
why not report it to the Emperor directly?

299
00:12:16,039 --> 00:12:17,159
Instead, you asked General Xiao

300
00:12:17,240 --> 00:12:18,080
to lead the troops to fight,

301
00:12:18,279 --> 00:12:18,919
to cover up the real purpose.

302
00:12:19,600 --> 00:12:20,960
And you went back to the capital to investigate privately.

303
00:12:21,879 --> 00:12:24,279
Although we have many shadow guards in the capital,

304
00:12:24,960 --> 00:12:26,600
it's not easy

305
00:12:26,840 --> 00:12:27,799
to find out the truth.

306
00:12:29,559 --> 00:12:31,080
If my brother trusts me enough,

307
00:12:31,799 --> 00:12:32,519
then eight years ago,

308
00:12:33,000 --> 00:12:34,159
I don't have to ask to leave the capital.

309
00:12:51,519 --> 00:12:52,320
In my dream,

310
00:12:53,360 --> 00:12:54,720
after I married the Second Prince,

311
00:12:54,919 --> 00:12:55,919
I was always alone in the room.

312
00:12:56,679 --> 00:12:57,799
until my mother died.

313
00:12:59,519 --> 00:13:00,679
I was bedridden

314
00:13:01,080 --> 00:13:02,519
and became foolish after waking up.

315
00:13:02,799 --> 00:13:03,840
I was humiliated.

316
00:13:05,559 --> 00:13:06,159
Go away!

317
00:13:06,600 --> 00:13:07,519
What bad luck!

318
00:13:09,600 --> 00:13:11,639
Zhiyan also disappeared during this period.

319
00:13:13,159 --> 00:13:14,000
After that,

320
00:13:14,639 --> 00:13:15,960
my father was wrongfully imprisoned.

321
00:13:16,639 --> 00:13:17,879
The whole family was killed.

322
00:13:19,080 --> 00:13:20,080
I was expelled to Lingguo Temple

323
00:13:20,080 --> 00:13:21,240
[and was under the protection of Consort Dowager Li.]

324
00:13:22,240 --> 00:13:23,919
[But she was killed half a month later.]

325
00:13:25,639 --> 00:13:27,000
[Is all this just an accident?]

326
00:13:30,039 --> 00:13:30,799
[Mu Jinghao,]

327
00:13:32,039 --> 00:13:32,799
[did you]

328
00:13:33,720 --> 00:13:35,120
[kill my mother]

329
00:13:36,039 --> 00:13:37,399
[and Consort Dowager Li?]

330
00:13:42,159 --> 00:13:43,639
[I can't think of many details now.]

331
00:13:46,440 --> 00:13:48,679
[Since I'm going to marry the Second Prince,]

332
00:13:49,559 --> 00:13:50,279
[the next thing]

333
00:13:51,799 --> 00:13:53,240
is the accident of my mother.

334
00:13:54,960 --> 00:13:55,320
Go.

335
00:13:56,720 --> 00:13:57,120
Go.

336
00:14:02,879 --> 00:14:03,440
What's wrong?

337
00:14:03,440 --> 00:14:03,879
Princess

338
00:14:04,200 --> 00:14:05,320
The carriage suddenly broke down.

339
00:14:05,480 --> 00:14:06,120
It can't go on.

340
00:14:06,559 --> 00:14:08,519
Please wait for a while.

341
00:14:08,679 --> 00:14:09,759
We'll go on after it's fixed.

342
00:14:10,559 --> 00:14:11,080
Well.

343
00:14:11,360 --> 00:14:12,480
I'm tired of sitting in the carriage.

344
00:14:13,360 --> 00:14:14,320
Watch your step.

345
00:14:14,320 --> 00:14:14,639
Okay.

346
00:14:16,159 --> 00:14:16,919
Take care.

347
00:14:17,440 --> 00:14:18,120
Go check

348
00:14:18,399 --> 00:14:19,240
what's wrong with the carriage.

349
00:14:20,360 --> 00:14:21,679
Why is it raining so hard?

350
00:14:24,080 --> 00:14:24,559
Mother.

351
00:14:24,559 --> 00:14:25,000
Sui'er.

352
00:14:27,840 --> 00:14:28,399
Watch out!
